move-it-shake-it-mousekedance-it-street-.name: Move It! Shake It! MousekeDance It! Street Party
move-it-shake-it-mousekedance-it-street-.sort_name: move it shake it mousekedance it street party
move-it-shake-it-mousekedance-it-street-.summary: Dance and sing along at the musical celebration for Mickey and Minnie featuring colorful floats and beloved Disney pals.

its-a-small-world.name: it's a small world
its-a-small-world.average_wait_assumes: Busy conditions with 30 or more boats operating
its-a-small-world.summary: Embark on a whimsical boat ride past a jubilant confection of singing children from around the globe.

astro-orbiter.name: Astro Orbiter
astro-orbiter.what_it_is: Buck Rogers-style rockets revolving around a central axis
astro-orbiter.when_to_go: Before 11 a.m. or during the last hour before closing.
astro-orbiter.summary: Pilot your very own spaceship high in the sky above Tomorrowland amid a gleaming constellation of orbiting planets.

flag-retreat.name: Flag Retreat
flag-retreat.ultimate_task: View from beginning until when flag is removed from pole.
flag-retreat.summary: Put your hand over your heart, follow the Pledge of Allegiance and hear patriotic songs as the flag is lowered and folded.

casey-jr-splash-n-soak-station.name: Casey Jr. Splash 'N' Soak Station
casey-jr-splash-n-soak-station.sort_name: casey jr splash n soak station
casey-jr-splash-n-soak-station.summary: Set the kids loose for fun under the sun at this whimsical water play area inspired by the circus train from Walt Disney’s Dumbo.

magic-kingdom-welcome-show.name: Let the Magic Begin
magic-kingdom-welcome-show.what_it_is: Characters and Dancing intro to the Magic Kingdom
magic-kingdom-welcome-show.ultimate_task: View full show from location where you can see characters.
magic-kingdom-welcome-show.summary: Taking place about 5 minutes before park opening on the Castle Forecourt Stage, this show features Disney characters who help guests get ready for the magical day that awaits them.

main-street-philharmonic.name: Main Street Philharmonic
main-street-philharmonic.summary: Hear this legendary marching band playing tunes from classic Disney films mixed with ragtime and swing.

prince-charming-regal-carrousel.name: Prince Charming Regal Carrousel
prince-charming-regal-carrousel.summary: Spin around, up and down to joyous music atop a regal steed at this classic attraction inspired by Disney’s Cinderella.

caseys-corner-pianist.name: Casey's Corner Pianist
caseys-corner-pianist.summary: This playful pianist bedazzles you with his impressive repertoire. Go ahead—make a request!

walt-disneys-carousel-of-progress.name: Walt Disney's Carousel of Progress
walt-disneys-carousel-of-progress.ultimate_task: View full show. Difficult to take a good photo.
walt-disneys-carousel-of-progress.summary: Travel through the 20th century to see how technology has improved our way of life during this classic, 21-minute Audio-Animatronics show.

town-square-theater-mickey-mouse.name: Meet Mickey Mouse at Town Square Theater
town-square-theater-mickey-mouse.ultimate_task: Autograph and photo with 1 character. If Mickey is used as core, Tinker Bell may be used as bonus.
town-square-theater-mickey-mouse.sort_name: meet mickey mouse at town square theater
town-square-theater-mickey-mouse.summary: Go backstage as a special guest of your pal, Mickey.

seven-dwarfs-mine-train.name: Seven Dwarfs Mine Train
seven-dwarfs-mine-train.when_to_go: First 30 minutes the park is open or use FastPass+.
seven-dwarfs-mine-train.summary: Race through the diamond mine from Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs on a swaying family coaster.

tomorrowland-speedway.name: Tomorrowland Speedway
tomorrowland-speedway.when_to_go: Before 10 a.m. or during last 2 hours before closing.
tomorrowland-speedway.summary: Put the pedal to the metal in your very own hotrod and cruise along a scenic miniature motorway.

mad-tea-party.name: Mad Tea Party
mad-tea-party.summary: Spin ‘round and ‘round in a giant pastel teacup during a madcap music-filled adventure.

frontierland-shootin-arcade.name: Frontierland Shootin' Arcade
frontierland-shootin-arcade.ultimate_task: Fire one full round of shots.
frontierland-shootin-arcade.summary: Test your gunnin’ skills at this rootin’, tootin’ wild west shooting gallery!

pirates-of-the-caribbean.name: Pirates of the Caribbean
pirates-of-the-caribbean.ultimate_task: Ride. Difficult to take a good photo.
pirates-of-the-caribbean.summary: Set sail on a swashbuckling voyage to a long-forgotten time and place when pirates and privateers ruled the seas.

enchanted-tales-with-belle.name: Enchanted Tales with Belle
enchanted-tales-with-belle.when_to_go: First hour the park is open, during parades or meal times.
enchanted-tales-with-belle.ultimate_task: Experience full tour and one story.
enchanted-tales-with-belle.summary: Relive the magic of Disney´s Beauty and the Beast during an unforgettable reenactment starring Belle, Lumiere... and you!

liberty-square-riverboat.name: Liberty Square Riverboat
liberty-square-riverboat.summary: Cruise the scenic Rivers of America aboard the Liberty Belle and take a gander at life in the U.S. over a century ago.

mickeys-royal-friendship-faire.name: Mickey's Royal Friendship Faire
mickeys-royal-friendship-faire.summary: See Mickey and his merry makers perform alongside other popular Disney pals during this magical, musical extravaganza.

dapper-dans.name: Dapper Dans
dapper-dans.ultimate_task: View for 5 minutes. Watching them on a Main Street Vehicle does NOT count.
dapper-dans.summary: This barbershop quartet spins harmonies as they play the chimes, tap dance and regale audiences with vaudeville humor.

haunted-mansion.name: The Haunted Mansion
haunted-mansion.ultimate_task: Ride. Difficult to take a good photo.
haunted-mansion.summary: Embark on a spine-tingling tour through an eerie haunted estate, home to ghosts, ghouls and supernatural surprises.

princess-fairytale-hall-rapunzel-tiana.name: Meet Rapunzel and Tiana at Princess Fairytale Hall
princess-fairytale-hall-rapunzel-tiana.when_to_go: Before 10:30 a.m., during parades, or in the evening just before the park closes.
princess-fairytale-hall-rapunzel-tiana.ultimate_task: Photo and autograph with 1 character here or from Elena queue as core. Other queue counts as a bonus.
princess-fairytale-hall-rapunzel-tiana.sort_name: meet rapunzel and tiana at princess fairytale hall

petes-silly-sideshow-minnie-daisy.name: Meet Dashing Disney Pals as Circus Stars at Pete’s Silly Side Show
petes-silly-sideshow-minnie-daisy.when_to_go: Before 11:30 a.m. or during the last 2 hours before closing.
petes-silly-sideshow-minnie-daisy.ultimate_task: Photo and autograph with 1 character here or from Goofy/Donald queue as core. Other queue counts as a bonus.
petes-silly-sideshow-minnie-daisy.sort_name: meet dashing disney pals as circus stars at petes silly side show
petes-silly-sideshow-minnie-daisy.summary: Some favorite Disney friends are waiting to meet you under the Big Top!

cosmic-dance-party.name: Cosmic Dance Party
cosmic-dance-party.summary: The Cosmic party is a space-themed character-fueled good time with loud music and flashing lights.

jungle-cruise.name: Jungle Cruise
jungle-cruise.when_to_go: Before 10 a.m. or 2 hours before closing, or use FastPass+
jungle-cruise.summary: Set sail for high adventure on a scenic boat tour of the most exotic and exciting rivers across Asia, Africa and South America.

dumbo-the-flying-elephant.name: Dumbo the Flying Elephant
dumbo-the-flying-elephant.summary: Soar high in the sky on a whimsical flight over Storybook Circus aboard Dumbo the Flying Elephant.

tom-sawyer-island.name: Tom Sawyer Island
tom-sawyer-island.what_it_is: Outdoor walk-through exhibit and rustic playground
tom-sawyer-island.ultimate_task: Fire rifle in Fort Langhorn, enter a cave, and walk on barrel bridge.
tom-sawyer-island.summary: Brave an adventure all your own at this rustic, secret hideaway inspired by the stories of Mark Twain.

magic-carpets-of-aladdin.name: The Magic Carpets of Aladdin
magic-carpets-of-aladdin.when_to_go: Before 10 a.m. or in the hour before park closing.
magic-carpets-of-aladdin.summary: Fly high over Agrabah on a magic carpet around a giant genie lamp.

monsters-inc-laugh-floor.name: Monsters, Inc. Laugh Floor
monsters-inc-laugh-floor.ultimate_task: View full show. If you can avoid it, you do NOT need to watch the pre-show video.
monsters-inc-laugh-floor.summary: Participate in the giggliest, most guffaw-friendly live comedy show ever—starring Monsters, Inc. and company!

minnies-wonderful-christmastime-firework.name: Minnie’s Wonderful Christmastime Fireworks
minnies-wonderful-christmastime-firework.summary: Minnie Mouse hosts a fireworks spectacular featuring several favorite holiday tunes.

ariels-grotto.name: Meet Ariel at Her Grotto
ariels-grotto.summary: The Little Mermaid greets friends from land and under the sea in a rocky coastal retreat.

town-square-theater-tinker-bell.name: Meet Tinker Bell at Town Square Theater
town-square-theater-tinker-bell.ultimate_task: Autograph and photo with 1 character. If used as core, Mickey may be used as bonus.
town-square-theater-tinker-bell.sort_name: meet tinker bell at town square theater
town-square-theater-tinker-bell.summary: Fly away to Main Street, U.S.A. where you can come face-to-face with a magical fairy from Pixie Hollow—it’s Tinker Bell!

under-the-sea.name: Under the Sea ~ Journey of the Little Mermaid
under-the-sea.when_to_go: Before 10:30 a.m., during the last 2 hours before closing, or use FASTPASS+.
under-the-sea.sort_name: under the sea journey of the little mermaid
under-the-sea.summary: Descend below the waves—without ever getting wet—for a whimsical musical adventure awash with scenes from the animated classic.

sorcerers-of-the-magic-kingdom.name: Sorcerers of the Magic Kingdom
sorcerers-of-the-magic-kingdom.what_it_is: Interactive video game in which players must defeat villains spread around different lands
sorcerers-of-the-magic-kingdom.ultimate_task: Start and complete 1 full mission as core. Each additional unique full mission counts as bonus. Maximum of 1 core and 8 bonus. Take photo completing last window of each mission. You may obtain cards in advance.
sorcerers-of-the-magic-kingdom.summary: Cast Merlin’s magical spells throughout Magic Kingdom park to defeat the dastardly Disney Villains who get in your way!

peter-pans-flight.name: Peter Pan's Flight
peter-pans-flight.when_to_go: First or last 30 minutes the park is open, or use FastPass+
peter-pans-flight.summary: Fly over London with Peter Pan aboard a magical pirate ship to Never Land.

barnstormer.name: The Barnstormer
barnstormer.when_to_go: Before 10:30 a.m., during parades, or in the evening just before the park closes.
barnstormer.summary: Take flight above Storybook Circus with Goofy and his homemade stunt airplanes for a thrilling, junior roller coaster ride.

a-pirates-adventure-treasures-of-seven-s.name: A Pirate's Adventure ~ Treasures of the Seven Seas
a-pirates-adventure-treasures-of-seven-s.when_to_go: Anytime, but after dark is better for the effects
a-pirates-adventure-treasures-of-seven-s.ultimate_task: Start and complete 1 full mission as core. Each additional unique full mission counts as bonus. Maximum of 1 core and 5 bonus (finale counts as a bonus mission). Take photo completing last step of each mission.
a-pirates-adventure-treasures-of-seven-s.sort_name: pirates adventure treasures of the seven seas
a-pirates-adventure-treasures-of-seven-s.summary: Join Captain Jack on an interactive adventure—take on missions, fend off fearsome foes and bring home a treasure of yer own!

walt-disney-world-railroad-frontierland-.name: Walt Disney World Railroad - Frontierland
walt-disney-world-railroad-frontierland-.what_it_is: Scenic railroad ride to Fantasyland or Main Street
walt-disney-world-railroad-frontierland-.special_needs: Rental strollers may not be taken on the Walt Disney World Railroad.
walt-disney-world-railroad-frontierland-.ultimate_task: Ride the full loop. Does not need to be continuous. As long as full track loop is covered, any stations may be used.
walt-disney-world-railroad-frontierland-.summary: Hear the prairie wind whisper sweet songs of the West as you chug from the frontier, around Magic Kingdom park, and back again.

once-upon-a-time.name: Once Upon a Time
once-upon-a-time.summary: Delight in a spellbinding nighttime show that brings Cinderella Castle to life with projections of beloved Disney scenes and characters.

splash-mountain.name: Splash Mountain
splash-mountain.when_to_go: As soon as the park opens, during afternoon or evening parades, just before closing, or use FastPass+
splash-mountain.summary: Take off on a rollicking log flume ride featuring characters and songs from the classic Disney film Song of the South.

princess-fairytale-hall-elena-cinderella.name: Meet Cinderella & Elena at Princess Fairytale Hall
princess-fairytale-hall-elena-cinderella.when_to_go: Before 10:30 a.m., during parades, or in the evening just before the park closes.
princess-fairytale-hall-elena-cinderella.ultimate_task: Photo and autograph with 1 character here or from Rapunzel queue as core. Other queue counts as a bonus.
princess-fairytale-hall-elena-cinderella.sort_name: meet cinderella elena at princess fairytale hall
princess-fairytale-hall-elena-cinderella.summary: Join Cinderella when she welcomes Elena to the land where 'a dream is a wish your heart makes.'

big-thunder-mountain-railroad.name: Big Thunder Mountain Railroad
big-thunder-mountain-railroad.when_to_go: Before 10 a.m., in the hour before closing, or use FastPass+
big-thunder-mountain-railroad.summary: Race through a haunted gold-mining town aboard a rollicking runaway mine train.

petes-silly-sideshow-goofy-donald.name: Meet Daring Disney Pals as Circus Stars at Pete's Silly Side Show
petes-silly-sideshow-goofy-donald.when_to_go: Before 11:30 a.m. or during the last 2 hours before closing.
petes-silly-sideshow-goofy-donald.ultimate_task: Photo and autograph with 1 character here or at Minnie/Daisy queue as core. Other queue counts as a bonus.
petes-silly-sideshow-goofy-donald.sort_name: meet daring disney pals as circus stars at petes silly side show
petes-silly-sideshow-goofy-donald.summary: Some favorite Disney friends are waiting to meet you under the Big Top!

space-mountain.name: Space Mountain
space-mountain.when_to_go: When the park opens, or use FastPass+
space-mountain.average_wait_assumes: Two tracks, one dedicated to FastPass+ riders, dispatching at 21-second intervals
space-mountain.ultimate_task: Ride. No queue games necessary. Difficult photo.
space-mountain.summary: Blast off on a rip-roaring rocket through the darkest reaches of outer space on this roller-coaster-type ride in the dark.

walt-disney-world-railroad-main-street-u.name: Walt Disney World Railroad - Main Street, U.S.A.
walt-disney-world-railroad-main-street-u.what_it_is: Scenic railroad ride around the perimeter of the Magic Kingdom, and transportation to Frontierland and Fantasyland.
walt-disney-world-railroad-main-street-u.special_needs: Only folded strollers are permitted on the train, so you can’t board with your rented Disney stroller. You can, however, obtain a replacement stroller at your destination. Just take your personal belongings, stroller name card, and rental receipt with you on the train.
walt-disney-world-railroad-main-street-u.ultimate_task: Ride the full loop. Does not need to be continuous. As long as full track loop is covered, any stations may be used.
walt-disney-world-railroad-main-street-u.sort_name: walt disney world railroad main street usa
walt-disney-world-railroad-main-street-u.summary: Celebrate classic Americana as you board a vintage train for a full circle tour of Magic Kingdom park.

festival-fantasy-parade.name: Disney Festival of Fantasy Parade
festival-fantasy-parade.when_to_go: Check the Times Guide - usually 3 pm
festival-fantasy-parade.ultimate_task: View each parade float from reasonable distances (there should be other parade-watchers near you). Take photo with first float and last float.
festival-fantasy-parade.summary: Celebrate the spirit of Disney as Magic Kingdom park comes alive with music and dance during a tribute to the tales of Fantasyland.

country-bear-jamboree.name: Country Bear Jamboree
country-bear-jamboree.when_to_go: Before 11:30 a.m., before a parade, or during the two hours before closing
country-bear-jamboree.probable_wait_time: This attraction is not terribly popular but has a comparatively small capacity. Waiting time between noon and 5:30 p.m. on a busy day will average 15-30 minutes.
country-bear-jamboree.ultimate_task: View full show. Photos only allowed at end of show.
country-bear-jamboree.summary: Have a knee-slappin’ good time at this jolly country-and-western show starring a hilarious bunch of singing bears.

swiss-family-treehouse.name: Swiss Family Treehouse
swiss-family-treehouse.ultimate_task: Walk through entire tree, from beginning to end.
swiss-family-treehouse.summary: Explore the ultimate treehouse—and behold breathtaking views—in this attraction inspired by the classic Disney film.

mickeys-philharmagic.name: Mickey's PhilharMagic
mickeys-philharmagic.when_to_go: Before 11 a.m., during parades, or use Fastpass if available
mickeys-philharmagic.ultimate_task: View full show. Difficult to take a good photo.
mickeys-philharmagic.summary: Get swept away in the magic of Disney animation in this 3D movie musical starring many favorite Disney characters.

many-adventures-of-winnie-the-pooh.name: The Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh
many-adventures-of-winnie-the-pooh.when_to_go: Before 10 a.m., in the 2 hours before closing, or use FastPass+
many-adventures-of-winnie-the-pooh.summary: Travel through Hundred Acre Wood in an oversized Hunny Pot and immerse yourself in the stories of Winnie the Pooh.

tomorrowland-transit-authority-peoplemov.name: Tomorrowland Transit Authority PeopleMover
tomorrowland-transit-authority-peoplemov.when_to_go: Anytime, but especially during hot, crowded times of day (11:30 a.m.-4:30 p.m.)
tomorrowland-transit-authority-peoplemov.summary: Embark on a 10-minute tour of Tomorrowland aboard this emission-free mass transit system of the future.

main-street-trolley-parade.name: Main Street Trolley Show
main-street-trolley-parade.summary: Watch these citizens pour out of a trolley during a lively performance welcoming you to the most magical place on earth!

happily-ever-after.name: Happily Ever After
happily-ever-after.summary: Experience a grand finale to your Disney day with the newest—and most spectacular—fireworks showcase in Magic Kingdom history!

frontierland-hoedown.name: Hoedown Happening
frontierland-hoedown.summary: Characters join square dancers and guests for a hoedown in front of the Country Bear Jamboree

enchanted-tiki-room.name: Walt Disney's Enchanted Tiki Room
enchanted-tiki-room.ultimate_task: View full show (pre-show not required). Difficult to take photo.
enchanted-tiki-room.summary: Tropical birds, Tiki gods and colorful flowers come to life in a swinging 10-minute South Seas musical celebration.

walt-disney-world-railroad-fantasyland-s.name: Walt Disney World Railroad - Fantasyland
walt-disney-world-railroad-fantasyland-s.what_it_is: Scenic railroad ride to Main Street U.S.A. and Frontierland.
walt-disney-world-railroad-fantasyland-s.special_needs: Rental strollers may not be taken on the Walt Disney World Railroad.
walt-disney-world-railroad-fantasyland-s.ultimate_task: Ride the full loop. Does not need to be continuous. As long as full track loop is covered, any stations may be used.
walt-disney-world-railroad-fantasyland-s.summary: Hop aboard this old-fashioned locomotive where dreams come true for a scenic tour of Magic Kingdom park.

hall-of-presidents.name: The Hall of Presidents
hall-of-presidents.probable_wait_time: The lines for this attraction look intimidating, but they're usually swallowed up as the theater exchanges audiences. Even during the busiest times, waits rarely exceed 40 minutes. ring busiest times, waits rarely exceed 40 mins.
hall-of-presidents.ultimate_task: View full show. Difficult to take a good photo.
hall-of-presidents.summary: Behold all 44 of the men who have served as U.S. President in an Audio-Animatronics show tracing the history of the United States.

buzz-lightyears-space-ranger-spin.name: Buzz Lightyear's Space Ranger Spin
buzz-lightyears-space-ranger-spin.when_to_go: First or last hour the park is open, or use FastPass+.
buzz-lightyears-space-ranger-spin.summary: Fire lasers to defeat Zurg in this shooting-gallery game that puts you in the center of a thrilling space battle.
